# Helm downloaded dependencies (reproducible via helm dependency build)
**/helm/charts/*.tgz

# Build and distribution output
**/dist/

# Go coverage profiles emitted by a module's `make unit-test`
*-coverage.out

# macOS
.DS_Store

# Go build output (each module builds to bin/ via its Makefile)
**/bin/
